summary: The app's health score remains stable at 74/100, with a weighted average rating of 3.7/5.0 based on 133 reviews. Users are generally having a good experience with the app, but are facing issues with customer support and technical problems. Investment features and user education are notable strengths.
pm_note: The PM team should prioritize resolving customer support issues and technical problems to improve the overall user experience and increase the app's health score.
